name: Portal Δ
description:
There is a pulsating portal calling for every soul. It has opened in the middle of nowhere, somewhere along the blockchain. You know you can't go through. But you know you have to. Everything is together down there. Everything is One and Endless. There's is a Portal Δ that has opened on the blockchain. 

MaxMSP/Jitter + modular synth + AE. 
960x960 px, 60 fps, H.264.
